%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant API as API Server
    participant Runner as runner binary
    participant Registry as OCI Registry

    Admin->>API: bencher runner create
    API-->>Admin: Runner + key
    Admin->>API: bencher spec create
    Admin->>API: bencher runner spec add
    Admin->>Runner: runner up --host --runner --key
    Runner->>API: Connect (WebSocket) and poll for Jobs
    API-->>Runner: Assign matching Job
    Runner->>Registry: Pull Image
    Registry-->>Runner: Image layers
    Runner->>Runner: Run benchmark
    Runner->>API: Submit results
